title: Alpha 10 commits
message:
Alpha 10 commits

Changelog:
1. Night mode: Automatically disable gesture recognition when you go to
sleep and automatically enable it when you wake up. To set the wake-up
and sleep time, enable Night Mode in Settings and set the wake-up and
sleep timings. This saves battery life substantially.
2. Inbuilt QuickCapture camera app:  Not exposed to user yet because
it's not fully ready for testing
3. Optimizations to code and some bug fixes
4. Improvements to Gesture Calibration: Added a help buttonï»¿

title: Alpha 7 commits
message:
Alpha 7 commits

Changelog:

1. Switched to rotation vector by default, accuracy and sensitivity
highly improved and chances of accidental launches significantly reduced
2. Added an option to change vibration intensity in Settings
3. Fixed camera launch due to vibration on notifications like messages,
etc
